{"entityMap":{},"blocks":[{"key":"c9j08","text":"Helping tax payers when they're due a refund","type":"header-one","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"cu6l1","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"59ega","text":"Some UK businesses collect Value Added Tax on the goods they sell. Those same businesses also pay VAT on some of the things they buy. When what they pay is greater than what they collect, HMRC will repay the difference. HMRC call this a \"box 5 refund\" or \"VAT repayment\".","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"fv94u","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"3g0dj","text":"Discovery","type":"header-two","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"df2as","text":"In 2018, fifty thousand people called asking \"where's my VAT repayment?\".  This demand meant that HMRC was spending £1.3 million yearly in telephony costs. ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"db86b","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"3g6qe","text":"If a user hadn't supplied bank details, HMRC had to send a cheque. This cost HMRC a further £1.7 million per year.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"5vdsr","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"25vgs","text":"Saving £3 million a year was the challenge HMRC asked us to solve.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"7hjrh","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"dne20","text":"Identifying the user need","type":"header-three","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"c48ta","text":"Our researcher, Kathy, led on several activities to better understand our users. Combining helpline data with user and stakeholder interviews she identified clear needs:","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"4fj9c","text":"Tell users how they'd get their repayment.","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"offset":11,"length":3,"style":"ITALIC"}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"6f5f","text":"Tell users when they'd get their repayment.","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"offset":11,"length":4,"style":"ITALIC"}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"e4fgt","text":"Tell users about any delay and inform them how to fix it.","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"offset":11,"length":5,"style":"ITALIC"}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"1g0v","text":"Tell users if HMRC had used repayments to offset other debt.","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"offset":11,"length":2,"style":"ITALIC"}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"a9ekd","text":"Tell users when HMRC had sent repayment.","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"offset":11,"length":4,"style":"ITALIC"}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"4oe4l","text":"Mapping the customer journey","type":"header-three","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"at3af","text":"A major challenge was picking our way through the various layers of HMRC. Lots of teams were involved in the VAT repayments process. We'd often have answers to questions which would spark more questions.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"550mk","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"a62ic","text":"I created a \"wall of knowledge\". We met daily to discuss finding, ask questions and update each other. ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"4od3q","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"7qt3f","text":"Over time we built a full map of the existing repayments experience. We added customer pain-points and opportunities as we discovered them.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"e3lri","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"5cqae","text":"Alpha","type":"header-two","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"984gb","text":"In alpha, we ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"8mkgn","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"14qfd","text":"A fresh perspective","type":"header-three","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"2cs5i","text":"I ran a workshop with user researchers, content designers and interaction designers. I invited people who knew very little about VAT repayments so I could use their fresh perspective.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"8culb","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"9oa65","text":"During the session I proposed two how might we questions:","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"offset":34,"length":12,"style":"ITALIC"}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"174gf","text":"How might we make calling HMRC the last thing people think of when worrying about their VAT repayments?","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"7or0j","text":"How might we repayments by cheque a thing of the past?","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"bcvl1","text":"The questions were intentionally focused. ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"fcmlr","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"b29ct","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"fmku1","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}]}